183
00:08:29,320 --> 00:08:30,515
- [all laughing]
- A damsel.

184
00:08:32,440 --> 00:08:36,593
- [hymn playing on church organ]
- [indistinct chattering]

185
00:08:41,520 --> 00:08:42,670
[Zari clears throat]

186
00:08:42,760 --> 00:08:46,151
If you don't jump that
buff coachman's bones, I will.

187
00:08:46,880 --> 00:08:49,600
