to catch a magical creature.

188
00:08:51,080 --> 00:08:52,912
[smacks lips] If that's the groom,

189
00:08:53,000 --> 00:08:54,434
then I'm glad I'm not the bride.

190
00:08:55,920 --> 00:08:58,674
