is still on mission.

217
00:10:27,840 --> 00:10:28,956
Okay.

218
00:10:29,040 --> 00:10:30,235
So, who did kill Hank?

219
00:10:31,160 --> 00:10:32,719
- [sighs] The demon.
- Okay, good.

