251
00:11:54,280 --> 00:11:55,280
Hmm?

252
00:11:55,840 --> 00:11:58,230
Fine, I'll go ask him some questions.

253
00:11:58,360 --> 00:12:00,431
- But that's it.
- You go get it, girl.

254
00:12:00,520 --> 00:12:01,715
Okay.

255
